Böhmes Volksthümliche Lieder

A collection of 704 German folk songs published by Franz Böhme in 1895. The songs were encoded by Helmuth Schaffrath as part of the Essen Folksong Collection.

Issues

  • Wrong titles

    The titles do not correspond to the titles used by Böhme. Instead, they are textual incipits as you can see on this online scan.

  • Missing page numbers

    There are no page numbers in the source files. We do have song numbers, which can be derived from the catalogue numbers.
